5ï¸âƒ£ Non-Functional Requirements (NFRs)

Scalability â†’ Cloud-based microservice architecture.
Security â†’ Encrypt resumes, JWT for auth, HTTPS APIs.
Performance â†’ Asynchronous calls between backend & ML service.
Maintainability â†’ Modular (Frontend â†” Backend â†” ML service).
Portability â†’ Deployable on AWS / Azure / GCP.
